      "note": "<div data-schema-version=\"9\"><h1>README</h1>\n<p>This collection is a catch-all for websites and academic papers that might be of interest to people reading my website. </p>\n<h2>How to use</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n(If on mobile) Send tab to computer\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Add website / blog post / paper to this collection</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\nIf paywalled, add archive: &lt;url&gt; to the <code>extra</code> field\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\nPeriodically export collection as better CSL JSON to Quarto and have listing filter the latest to display\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n</div>",
